r.s: High Performance Programmatic Server for PHP with Async IO, Coroutines and Fibers
r.d: Build high-performance, scalable, concurrent TCP, UDP, Unix Socket, HTTP, WebSocket services with PHP and easy to use coroutine, fibers API.
r.n: . Fix postgres client metaData api bugs . Fix cookie parsing bug causing cookie errors . Fix memory leak in swoole_stream_select . Fix compatible issues with old libcurl on centos 7 . Fix compatible issues for PHP 8.0 and Fedora, Centos 7
